Title: Spiderwebs
Plot: Dawson comes through with No Doubt concert tickets, but he and Natasha's first public date ends in a brush with the law. Joey and Eddie have to sneak into the concert, while Pacey come to blows with CJ at the concert when it is revealed that he slept with Audrey.
ParentalRatingReason: PG Violence, coarse language and sexual references
GuestStars: No Doubt, Cydnee Welburn, Kathleen Thompson-Parker, Stuart Ward, Steve DuMouchel, Jim Grimshaw, Donny De Castro, John Copeman
